                        <small>Business Traveler</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="testimonial-card p-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-stars mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="testimonial-text">"The view from our room was breathtaking. The hotel amenities are top-notch and the location is perfect."</p>
                    <div class="testimonial-author">
                        <h6 class="mb-0">Sarah Johnson</h6>
                        <small>Family Vacation</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="testimonial-card p-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-stars mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-star-half text-warning"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p class="testimonial-text">"We celebrated our anniversary here and it was a wonderful experience. The staff made our stay truly special."</p>
                    <div class="testimonial-author">
                        <h6 class="mb-0">Michael & Lisa</h6>
                        <small>Couple</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
